            "pub_date": "2025-03-27 23:31:38",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "上水夫妻為錢嘈 躁夫鐵錘手腳並用打妻被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"上水夫妻為錢嘈 躁夫鐵錘手腳並用打妻被捕\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/495d0c9926106e2e19079617b9f391d4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250327/_2025032723125174979.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">上水夫妻為錢嘈 躁夫鐵錘手腳並用打妻被捕</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>上水有丈夫因金錢問題，用手腳及鐵錘打妻被捕。事發於周四（3月27日）下午5時許，警方於上水智昌路13號一街市對開，發現一名42歲姓范女子手腳受傷但清醒，遂安排她送北區醫院治理。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方調查後，懷疑婦人早前在上水圍大元村一村屋，因金錢問題與丈夫爭執，其間懷疑被丈夫以鐵錘及手腳襲擊。經初步調查後，45歲姓江丈夫涉嫌襲擊致造成身體傷害（AOABH）被捕，現在被扣留調查。案件由大埔警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
